    <p><strong>Daily Devotions<br>
    </strong>One idea for using the daily reflective devotionals (that all office based workers should be doing together daily) is to use a chapter of Hebrews (This months reading) for the meditation experience. In the Kapiti office I often do it alone and find it very worthwhile. </p>
